_sText:
Aim Temple is a small, well-lit temple map, perfect for those short but fierce matches, or just for goofing around.

A well-hidden easter egg can be triggered on this map- but unless you're noclipping or speedhacking, you'll need a friend to help you trigger it. Your reward will be hearing the manliest song in the history of man.

Good luck finding it, and have fun on Aim Temple!
